high_descs: Turn around and face the end of the brown desk.
Pick the the CD from the end of the desk.
Turn to the left and walk across the room, then turn right to face the dresser in the corner.
Place the CD on top of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Move the CD from the desk to the top of the dresser.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the desk.
Pick up the CD closest to the side of the desk you're facing.
Turn left and walk to the far wall, then turn right and face the dresser.
Put the CD on the dresser to the right of the safe.
anns.task_desc: Place a CD on a dresser.

high_descs: Pick up cd from bottom left hand corner of desk.
Turn left, go across room.  Turn right, go to dresser.
Place cd on top of dresser, to the right of the white object.
anns.task_desc: Move cd from desk to dresser.
